description:
Three loops - three perspectives on an ethereal subject - composed of particles, light and sound.
// The sound of each piece complements to one whole soundscape when played back together.
// Ideally watched on three displays and listend to with headphones. 
// The loops are embedded in an HTML Player so simultaneous playback inside hicetnunc’s gallery view is possible 
